                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.7331A15/19: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Venezuela</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Engert</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-05-17T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 17, 1929—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>16. If you believe such action necessary you may informally remind the Venezuelan
                    Government as suggested in confidential paragraph your telegram No. 36 of May
                    13, 10 a.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
